All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Capsule
This class represents a capsule, which is a small piece of content that can be shared on a platform.
Collaborator
The Collaborator class represents a person who collaborates in a project.
ControllerProjects
The ControllerProjects class manages a collection of Project objects.
Manager
The Manager class is usefull to create managers to be assigned to a project.
Project
This class represents a Project.
Stage
The Stage class represents a stage of a project, containing capsules with information about it.
SystemGreen
The SystemGreen class is the main class for the GreenSQA data system.
TypeCapsule
The TypeCapsule enum represents the different types of capsules that can be assigned to a project.
TypeStage
The TypeStage enum represents the different types of stages that a project can have.
